00:34:59,533 --> 00:35:04,877
And they're being told that only 77% of players have three reports.

596
00:35:04,877 --> 00:35:07,238
Well, 77% of players have less than three reports.

597
00:35:07,864 --> 00:35:10,446
But you might view that as, okay, that's good.

598
00:35:10,446 --> 00:35:13,048
But it could also be telling you that over 20% of people

599
00:35:13,048 --> 00:35:14,829
have more than three reports.

600
00:35:14,829 --> 00:35:17,552
Maybe I don't need to be so nice.

601
00:35:17,552 --> 00:35:19,634
And certainly in research where they've shown people

602
00:35:19,634 --> 00:35:22,136
in neighborhoods energy use, where you get to see,

