00:38:48,643 --> 00:38:51,465
And the more people that have these experience boosts

659
00:38:51,465 --> 00:38:52,747
on your side when you're playing,

660
00:38:52,747 --> 00:38:56,049
the faster everyone's experience goes outside of the game.

